data.name: Premier Investment Term Deposit
data.description: Rewarding you with higher interest on balances over $5,000. Enjoy the security of a fixed rate for your nominated term

features.additionalInfo: Easy reinvestment, with automatic rollover at maturity for your choice of term
Choose how and when you receive interest payments - reinvest or transfer to another bank account
Arrange to reinvest your interest payments or transfer your interest to another account
Use internet or mobile banking to check your balance
Access your funds prior to maturity by providing 31 days prior notice to redeem your account early (an interest adjustment and early payout fee apply)
All deposits up to $250,000 are protected by the Federal Government's deposit guarantee, so your savings are secure with us
Choose the length of your term, from just one month
For monthly interest payments, the applicable interest rate will be the rate listed above less 0.10% p.a.
Earn higher interest if you deposit $5,000 or more

eligibility.additionalInfo: A citizen or permanent resident of Australia;
Eighteen (18) years of age or over
Applying for a personal account and not in the name of a business or trust. There should be no more than two account holders for this account

fees.name: Early payout fee
fees.additionalInfo: Fee charged for for early redemption

depositRates.additionalInfo: Interest is calculated on the daily closing balance of your account and paid monthly or end of term. For monthly interest payments the applicable interest rate will be the rate quoted above less 0.10% with a minimum rate of 0.05% p.a
